{"tid":869454,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打又炒人","createTime":"2018-10-20T10:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T05:37:23.000Z","uid":30788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a78e069d78b4b259c3eb93449442fd2d5e2afa8d","tid":869454,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"銀行裁員】傳渣打裁員不逾300人 月底公佈<br />\n<br />\n傳渣打裁員應付投資者壓力(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》引述消息人士指出，渣打集團正準備新一輪裁員削減成本計劃，以應付投資者不滿公司表現的壓力。裁員計劃可能於今個月公佈第三季業績時發佈。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息指，裁員計劃涉及中東及非洲分部，削減最多300名員工。另一位消息人士指，為了節省成本，該銀行更凍結部分招聘名額，及限制員工外派。<br />\n渣打發言人表示，該行下半年支出將與上半年相若，這一點將會於10月31日公佈的第三季業績時確認。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"2d75dfe7e82cf81af9acef910635e7f28ee62aa9","tid":869454,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:24:16.000Z","msg":"炒人會利好股價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25a93cdacec7dcc87cb90992f04bf0165320571","tid":869454,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f478262b0da7a26a9cdfb920c920369bfb3df8","tid":869454,"uid":134438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"炒人兼大跌 只有渣打做得到"},{"pid":"67bb94c028f6f90e35f6735a48a526a5e9a212f7","tid":869454,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"投資者不滿公司表現的壓力=要炒員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b095e922df01da1c8e6a8a4291a47556669af12","tid":869454,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e54b318fcf510afd0ba44ddc6b7127bd87066c45","tid":869454,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d75dfe7e82cf